      • getCandidateElements

        com.google.common.collect.ImmutableList<CandidateElement> getCandidateElements()
        Returns:
        A list of CandidateElement that might have been fired during the crawl. If an event was fired it is registered as an Eventable an can be retrieved from StateFlowGraph.getAllEdges(). If the candidates were not set because of an error it returns null.
